Authorization Grant - 
	1. Authorization code
		-- client directs resource owner to authorization server
		-- authorization server authenticates reource owner and provides authorization code
		-- resource owner provides authorization code to client
	2. Implicit
		-- client doesn't get an authorization code it gets an access token directly
	3. Resource owner password credentials
		-- client gets resource owner's username/password (only if resource owner absolutely trust clients)
	4. Client credentials
		